{"obj_edit_time":"1769159720","blocks":[{"block_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb","block_type":1,"children":["doxjpL98OuHT7eAOU8g1lT6WjXg","doxjpUzpaTXWqagop2JhNt9lAdg","doxjpDX1h89ho0cnR5E45d3dRDe","doxjpi0uAKE6kI0tVBRUKJpS2Le","doxjpLDdz4PNrZynqS6JQQypdHh","doxjpckNwbHuArGyPYfv0Dub7fb","doxjp9KJfvQroUNhTMKkwd5uLAm","doxjpwPOwM78Op7PCGKvVFGoBAc"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1 餘額通","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxjpL98OuHT7eAOU8g1lT6WjXg","block_type":14,"code":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"slug: G09Dw7B53iGuRxkyJfccDWOknyH\ntitle: 9.1 餘額通\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"sidebar_position: 1","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"language":67,"wrap":false}},"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb"},{"block_id":"doxjpUzpaTXWqagop2JhNt9lAdg","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1 餘額通","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb"},{"block_id":"doxjpDX1h89ho0cnR5E45d3dRDe","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1A 問：餘額通觸發自動贖回規則是什麼？能用作抵扣認購其他基金、申購 IPO？","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb"},{"block_id":"doxjpi0uAKE6kI0tVBRUKJpS2Le","block_type":2,"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"答：1.基金是每個交易日都會產生申贖渠道單，但是交收（回填）依賴基金公司實際返回申購確認份額，贖回確認金額的時間，基金那邊設定了 T+幾只是展示用的；客戶購買了股票，T+2 需要交收股票，買完股票後現金可提會變成負數，此時會立刻觸發餘額通自動贖回，T+1 基金公司會打款到賬，當天要人工在 WBO 完成清算交收，這樣客戶帳戶上就有錢作 T+2 的股票交收了。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpLDdz4PNrZynqS6JQQypdHh","block_type":2,"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"2.理論上不能買基金，因為購買基金當天就要客戶扣款，然後把錢打給基金公司，等不到餘額通贖回。 IPO 使用餘額通有時間限制，如果用戶認購 IPO 時間晚於認購截止日的前一個交易日上午 9:00，因為餘額通贖回金額到帳時間晚於認購截止日，就不能用餘額通直接打新，用作抵扣美股港股則沒問題。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpckNwbHuArGyPYfv0Dub7fb","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1B 問：設置了最小贖回份額為整數，為什麼能贖回小數份額？","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb"},{"block_id":"doxjp9KJfvQroUNhTMKkwd5uLAm","block_type":2,"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"答：餘額通標的，贖回時只判斷持股份額，不判斷最小賣出份額/金額限制。\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"自動贖回是用於償還欠款或交收的資金，如果無法自動贖回會導致客戶欠款。所以餘額通贖回時不受最小賣出份額/金額的限制。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpwPOwM78Op7PCGKvVFGoBAc","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":308,"token":"TIlubmPiuoU6pnxWqZZjSaSDpxc","width":1640},"parent_id":"IsdidhfuSo6EEmxRHU8jPZIypwb"}]}